{"tid":276113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"得中五，頂唔順自己人工，想進修。。","createTime":"2017-06-08T14:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T00:26:12.000Z","uid":89751,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b1a6b2ec22b470214e2a28b7b51076e7fa2ba6","tid":276113,"uid":89751,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"話說小女得中五，讀完書做左文職已10年，講真，我冇乜學歷，萬二真係頂盡！我而家都30歲，想進修下，希望可以有萬五六蚊，好喇！問題黎喇，我對科科都冇興趣，而且就算要我讀，都想搵啲實用啲，好似健康， 營養學文憑嗰啲，但為咗張文憑一陣見工嘅時候又問你：點解你讀嗰樣又唔係做番嗰樣？<br />\n其實我只係想要咗張沙紙， 要我讀工商管理市場學嗰啲我覺得冇咩用，我只係想打份正正常常嘅工，我冇咩野心， 只係我覺得而家就算普通文員嘅都要中七畢業，我唔使做到主管位置，但都咁難。。<br />\n我應該點做好？"},{"pid":"ce472458dee126fb9ffe14b9ea7a0d8a2a967054","tid":276113,"uid":26522,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"ｐｔｇｆ"},{"pid":"a6248184fd3a8ec3d5c0a9ebc3109b3b4acb0ec2","tid":276113,"uid":33325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"有乜專長/興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb662a2976715a9923c874dfef09e3e01345d23","tid":276113,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ｐｔｇｆ</blockquote><br />\nFtgf"},{"pid":"9ccf418cc558e1dd1d0eac2945fdfc2a23af88e7","tid":276113,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"最緊要有讀番書既意志<br />\n冇既話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41138174fcfeb2129e2490c84557ed314e55754d","tid":276113,"uid":29087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"做地盤 唔好曬時間"},{"pid":"176b6e6316d312fb552ea0da6360dac4025168af","tid":276113,"uid":9923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"護理個啲囉<br />\n但你無心讀既話<br />\n考完又唔合格都係無用"},{"pid":"c25d70419810c6edda2760625a7838d0c580b159","tid":276113,"uid":71248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"讀個毅進 考紀律部隊🤘🏻"},{"pid":"00c45cb7e7963e531d70094132601d73296fec25","tid":276113,"uid":86438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"你講到自己出發點只為多4千人工 16000夠哂 咁你乜都唔洗讀 去做洗碗咪得<br />\n<br />\n你諗得讀書 即係都想學返專業技能 唔再做普通文員仔 做d別人難以取代既 咁你首先要諗下自己想做邊行 累積個一行經驗<br />\n<br />\n當你知自己想做邊行 就自然知要讀咩"},{"pid":"5f352b6b92d3138c7e2dab88196e97643dadee1d","tid":276113,"uid":9447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"土木工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2fa10a9fad287b2c6fb5b7a38f1d9270718050","tid":276113,"uid":89751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"應該咁講，文員而家都唔會請中五，我就係冇想讀啲乜，搵份萬五六嘅文員我都OK。。<br />\n我就係冇咩出發點先煩！<br />\n我其實返開五天工作，近日搵五天工作都要中七，專上學歷，所以先話要左張沙紙求份普通工！"},{"pid":"42c437cfe0c27460d5bd4bbf94bbc765564ad7ff","tid":276113,"uid":42735,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"12000蚊點生存"},{"pid":"d3b6701f5e05826fb599b8f31fb97df541f0d38e","tid":276113,"uid":40131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"唔好做文員囉..文員偏低"},{"pid":"f11f584ff37d320c952844fc13e66b0b22cf1094","tid":276113,"uid":65710,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"讀護士啦"},{"pid":"317e8de4b6c2c805ec72c5f1e1835a4d6cce981f","tid":276113,"uid":92063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"讀完唔代表你就會搵到萬五六<br />\n都要睇你有無能力搵萬五六"},{"pid":"e51ce428e05ac00465520ad19aa848b095965034","tid":276113,"uid":20302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:03:17.000Z","msg":"你讀完書都仲諗搵番萬5萬6既文員？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你根本就對自己冇信心  又冇大志 <br />\n連自己目標都唔知 成30歲人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你平時俾人屌得少？"},{"pid":"f7c68f3a53625cbfefba781f377e4dc7be735a93","tid":276113,"uid":86438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"去i大讀dip hdip 但我驚你讀完有排先搵得返d學費<br />\n<br />\n讀得黎不如早d嫁左佢做師奶算啦"},{"pid":"42b18651430a3a19e4daba2446ae8b9ed4ccd5f3","tid":276113,"uid":62424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"進修又點？又唔係大學學位。<br />\n人工同學歷唔一定成正比既<br />\n如果唔介意輪更 不如去做機場保安 萬四以上"},{"pid":"a91e18e7e0f5fe3c897345f9a93b5fa6735fd5f9","tid":276113,"uid":57117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"會考合格走走做政苦啦 康民處都有13k up"},{"pid":"db19d1c00c95788eeabb676b752bd473bde77ebf","tid":276113,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"搵個老襯嫁左佢好d"},{"pid":"69ae8b01580a94f73a8f97bd36347d8dec691b6b","tid":276113,"uid":6250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"我都係得中五<br />\n報左個PCA課程諗住係醫院做呀姐算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申有情緒病廢青中五學期頭hea到依家無做野"},{"pid":"25175f62b1a56324debcffbe9a2283e6c40fd251","tid":276113,"uid":89751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"就係男友都唔搵得多。<br />\n我本身都諗住上年嫁人，我最後冇揀到有錢嘅(脾氣超差)，揀左個脾氣好，冇乜錢嘅，本身我唔大洗，一個月用2000蚊，3000蚊家用，5000儲，但儲5000太少，想搵多少少，儲10000都好。<br />\n為求穩定，準時收工，五天工作就OK。<br />\n因為公司就結業，想留都冇得留！<br />\n出面而家10000蚊一個月仲要返六天，點解咁可悲？"},{"pid":"9f20576c64f836452785d90dd6e52153b4632dda","tid":276113,"uid":17836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"咁你唔報政府ACO/CA? 女既話好易入。"},{"pid":"ff6cb2f85775c6a14f2774a3cc17c82f3340fe82","tid":276113,"uid":89751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會考合格走走做政苦啦 康民處都有13k up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我英文打字肥左，其餘三樣都PASS晒。<br />\n我練極都唔合格！我屎波"},{"pid":"5f24f6d709f8452079dfa75ca7491320c3a826fa","tid":276113,"uid":29080,"