s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真以樓主能力考ACO啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中英文打字其實都唔係咁難啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係有心嘅出去報下英文Course增值下自己 年紀唔係藉口"},{"pid":"8716f4f843118cdf89aeea5cbb17e5ff0f09ecd3","tid":276113,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊去灣仔碼頭跳海<br />\n<br />\n我本來讀大學<br />\n<br />\n會計 hons degree<br />\n<br />\n點撚知自己ON99 QUIT撚左<br />\n<br />\n真係衰衝動<br />\n<br />\n..................<br />\n<br />\n成世一件好事都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n......................................</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncity?"},{"pid":"d553f519923af4cf4d4405c864a03961f8602ebe","tid":276113,"uid":80719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家陣香港一街大學生都難搵食 中學學歷真係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真以樓主能力考ACO啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中英文打字其實都唔係咁難啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係有心嘅出去報下英文Course增值下自己 年紀唔係藉口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果只係aim 1516k，我覺得樓主唔洗咁灰心。冇學歷既話咁唯有做野落力d，靠經驗壓制下，肯學肯做搵呢個數唔會太難，最緊要唔好輕易放棄，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67672b82a1c36a61a29688b2662b56782996e0f5","tid":276113,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:19:43.000Z","msg":"去做順豐咪得，大把囡囡走去做"},{"pid":"0e2d354a45b247ac2a98e4b6985b27a3fb53e163","tid":276113,"uid":18385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"ACO la<br />\n英文打字 2年夠練返黎"},{"pid":"f0f24e4740a799fd40522f4234fbcc30c142cef3","tid":276113,"uid":89751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"ACO再考多次我係會。唔得我真係收得皮。<br />\n我其實做過政府合約，可惜係HQs Fund，冇得續！"},{"pid":"bf7158fc2409dca7c0f11c604755d59290787fee","tid":276113,"uid":17964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"知恥近乎勇<br />\n每一個人目標同著眼點都唔同<br />\n唔好太在意同人比較<br />\n搵自己興趣，想去進修就去進修，增值自己永遠係最好嘅投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474961306f1a894ecb2d7708dd1530b72597e7f9","tid":276113,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"讀完書你想做咩先？<br />\n做返文員唔會因爲你多張沙紙就加你人工囉<br />\n同埋5日工真係唔多"},{"pid":"f152aca699ea17b0f251bc3a9d343e9a295c9318","tid":276113,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"三十歲，就黎高危產婦，仲想拖？<br />\n結婚生仔等幾年拎公屋好過啦<br />\n想唔生仔都得，住老豆老母度囉<br />\n等唔知幾時排到公屋<br />\n筆錢就夠用黎裝修<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人無遠慮必有近憂<br />\n<br />\n同窮撚一齊有一套方法<br />\n<br />\n同有錢仔一齊又有另一種相處方法<br />\n<br />\n恕我直言，你咁天真又迷茫既思考方式<br />\n就算你冇飛個有錢仔，競爭對手咁多，最後佢都係會飛左你"},{"pid":"1c7313df6fe44de1c4b7bc24a4fb8b1db0495480","tid":276113,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"你比錢+時間去讀，time cost 都唔止啦"},{"pid":"fe4a733d1865cfdf70b894f0b366c911d07c0fc1","tid":276113,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"女警啦 兩皮幾等緊你"},{"pid":"b222e5ebb75c889a9fd1add401e33c36f7520446","tid":276113,"uid":35160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主真係好撚廢<br />\nA又唔得B又唔得<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連強項文員都唔識打英文 真係笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb58d5104089f8c3c793a6eb13ea7d146ff438c6","tid":276113,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>將你進修果d錢拎去投資好過啦<br />\n今時今日進唔進修都唔係重點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都有諗過，但唔知點入手</blockquote><br />\n自己同另一半仲有屋企人好好傾下計劃下，如果你係唔識既話，唔好亂咁信街外人，記住一條general rule, 就係現代經濟係靠借錢谷起既，你搵兩蚊最多都係洗兩蚊，但如果你搵兩蚊借一蚊就可以洗三蚊，而你既支出係另一個人既收入，收入加貸款做本金係一定大過單收入，會有好多人叫你借錢，但你收入唔多經驗唔多，好易俾人呃，所以唔好借錢投資就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之，你借左還得到你就實賺到，但你借左還唔到就仆硬街。<br />\n<br />\n另一個事實就係，有錢人唔洗進修，窮人俾錢進修繼續窮。"},{"pid":"23c4974b2c7f9ff72b65d0e6fbea29298b8213b1","tid":276113,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"我會考得三分 果時都唔知讀書為乜 ，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家好後悔，要追番哂所有野係好辛苦 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會考三分去讀左個四年HD ,出到黎第一份工去左做陳豪幫人裝上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、人工得8900 、心諗份工都係冇前途 、又冇得升職 。咁讀書黎有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後做左唔夠一個月轉行去左做IT 人工都係九千。<br />\n之後好比心機做，做左三年人工加左三次去到萬五。<br />\n到果時想搵工send左十幾份CV都冇回音 ，之後發現全部都要大學畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  心諗原來冇張沙紙HR唔係睇唔起你、係睇你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻拿拿林走去出面搵左個PT degree讀左兩年，放左工都要讀書辛苦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。之後終於有公司請 ，人工亦去到兩萬，之後又做左兩年 ，依家人工去到二萬中到。 要追返真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b508e9e0aef3f2efd15b8ef18f6eec03c60ac6f6","tid":276113,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"去學門手藝<br />\n<br />\n例如 油漆 1600-2000一間大屋"},{"pid":"5630cf381abde95400d61eecc8a667afd6a9b433","tid":276113,"uid":9477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"